name: Sidewalk
description:
Original atrt by Lisha Ruan.

I am a 26-year-old artist living in Maryland, USA. My art seeks to capture the simultaneously symbiotic and tense relationship between order and chaos. Creation and destruction, are simultaneously flip sides of a coin and the same thing. In art, as in life, I seek encounters with what we most love and what we most fear.

Thanks for checking out my art, hope you have a great day.
